  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Build A Restaurant</strong></h2><br>Start with a small plot of land and build your restaurant from the ground up. Once you have made enough money, you can buy more land and expand. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/175f6a730e573e69c484b1effff7aff1.poster.avif?t=1727452600\" width=600 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/175f6a730e573e69c484b1effff7aff1.webm?t=1727452600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/175f6a730e573e69c484b1effff7aff1.mp4?t=1727452600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Make It Beautiful</strong></h2><br>Guests want more than just good food - they care about your restaurant decor too. Make sure your restaurant is well decorated to keep them happy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/3d2c69df06217ef103a20a2f4d76bd17.poster.avif?t=1727452600\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/3d2c69df06217ef103a20a2f4d76bd17.webm?t=1727452600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/3d2c69df06217ef103a20a2f4d76bd17.mp4?t=1727452600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Manage Your Employees</strong></h2><br>A good team is the core of every successful business. Hire the right employees and set their priorities wisely. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/cceb1ceaf8ee07e0ab11fe5d3e74ec8f.poster.avif?t=1727452600\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/cceb1ceaf8ee07e0ab11fe5d3e74ec8f.webm?t=1727452600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/cceb1ceaf8ee07e0ab11fe5d3e74ec8f.mp4?t=1727452600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Keep It Clean</strong></h2><br>It’s important to keep your restaurant clean. Guests will not be thrilled about the presence of rats.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/1ae4ba808ee3442358d6e124519a726d.poster.avif?t=1727452600\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/1ae4ba808ee3442358d6e124519a726d.webm?t=1727452600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/1ae4ba808ee3442358d6e124519a726d.mp4?t=1727452600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Expand The Menu</strong></h2><br>Creating a menu seems simple, but a poorly thought-out menu is the death of many restaurants. Pick your dishes carefully and make sure they are the right price.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/5ca1189cca63c12825b07972572b52dd.poster.avif?t=1727452600\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/5ca1189cca63c12825b07972572b52dd.webm?t=1727452600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/5ca1189cca63c12825b07972572b52dd.mp4?t=1727452600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customer Is King</strong></h2><br>Make sure customers are satisfied by meeting all their needs. Don’t leave them waiting too long, have plenty of restrooms, serve high quality food, and more. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/3d6ea53dc2d59bd3da83b439567a4082.poster.avif?t=1727452600\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/3d6ea53dc2d59bd3da83b439567a4082.webm?t=1727452600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/3d6ea53dc2d59bd3da83b439567a4082.mp4?t=1727452600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Beat The Scenarios</strong></h2><br>TasteMaker contains six scenarios that offer unique challenges. Do you have what it takes to succeed?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/e84da8c11122b9c003092ed042c5ea67.poster.avif?t=1727452600\" width=614 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/e84da8c11122b9c003092ed042c5ea67.webm?t=1727452600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1289340/extras/e84da8c11122b9c003092ed042c5ea67.mp4?t=1727452600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>",
